      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A steel curse previously destroyed all the worldâ€™s steel which left the population defenseless and now three years later, black iron gates randomly appeared in each major city, resulting in monster hordes which killed many. A dungeon lays behind these gates and your task as the hero is to reach the bottom and save the world. Unfortunately, a lot of the game's story is shown at the very beginning with small updates as you reach additional levels of the dungeon, which left me wanting to know more. I did discover that with this game being part of the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Spellsword",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " series, there was another game called ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Demontide",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to learn more lore of the series, as well as through the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Spellsword",
