            "text": "is a game that you can play while in transit that makes use of the touch screen and will always feel fresh whenever you have a run due to the nature of the genre. While there is a downside that comes in the form of a basic story, the sound design team really went above and beyond when setting up the theme and giving actions impact. Overall, itâ€™s a fun take on the deck building genre with a dark fantasy setting that will keep you coming back for more runs.",
